Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:21.04,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:20.36,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:11.15,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:14.19,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with her Soul Protect on, I can tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:18.45,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That Medusa is behind this door.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:21.07,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:24.16,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:26.54,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,May I have a glass of water?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:28.29,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:34.92,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Medusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:38.01,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a girl's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:40.09,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something I can do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:42.18,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:44.47,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:46.52,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:49.31,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault that Crona's suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:52.10,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're Crona's friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:54.15,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,How is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:58.32,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you've been using Crona all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:00.74,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so worried about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:03.41,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always been such a weak child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:05.28,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you make her do such things?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:07.29,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You dare call yourself a parent?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:10.33,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's possible, I'd like to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:13.17,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long since I last saw her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:15.84,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop playing dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:19.42,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I wonder what she will say...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:21.22,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,if she sees me like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:23.05,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to stop playing dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.14,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Maka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:28.22,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:32.44,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless, talking to someone like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:34.94,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Medusa,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:38.07,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,enjoy the rest of your life in this dark cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:40.40,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an end befitting for the likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:43.03,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.79,0:03:57.50,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I don't think it will end like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:02.34,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you agree, Professor Stein?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:14.52,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the Cards: Medusa Surrenders to Shibusen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:18.94,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, that was really unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:21.74,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would've thought that she was still alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:24.95,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,moreover, surrender to Shibusen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:26.91,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:33.04,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But that time, we definitely finished her off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:36.33,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're talking about witches here,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:38.88,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,so anything is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:41.51,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The problems start here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:42.47,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.88,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Medusa that we're talking about here,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:48.22,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,we cannot deal with her using ordinary methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.85,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:55.14,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:58.82,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can walk out of here just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:02.24,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The world itself has begun to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:03.78,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:06.11,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,you should know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:10.49,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not place a bet on something does not guarantee my winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:11.99,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:14.50,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Professor Stein?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:16.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Your voice is trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:22.46,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pitiful, seeing the madness slowly consuming you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:25.68,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really the time for you to be worrying about others?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:28.68,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:32.22,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,So join me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:37.69,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you didn't surrender so that you could tell me all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:40.77,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as you are bound by the laws,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.57,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll never be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:45.15,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:49.12,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Together, we shall witness the dawn of a new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:52.45,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:54.37,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:57.71,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:01.17,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to interrupt your conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:03.84,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home, Stein.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:06.05,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You should still be under house arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:16.52,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me, Medusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:22.19,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:29.11,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to be the one interrogating me, Death Scythe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:35.16,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mister, why am I dressed up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:37.50,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,My hands hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:38.66,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:40.04,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not falling for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:41.33,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:44.13,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But you talked to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:46.01,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,At least now I'm one step ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:50.26,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you talk as much as you like soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:00.39,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:02.19,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:04.19,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless to get information out of me through torture.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:04.98,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:09.86,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot do anything to my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:12.70,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,For you see, this body is "borrowed".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:16.87,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about infiltration and takeover, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:22.29,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,As a parent, you should know too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.75,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Give that body back already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:28.30,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only borrowing this body until my magic power fully recovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:29.92,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return it, eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:32.72,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never cease being a low-life, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:35.39,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is it really okay for you to say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:40.10,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I might just turn out to be your savior, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:41.14,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:45.65,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm holding some information that is very useful for Shibusen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:47.36,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Information?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:51.99,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:53.28,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop with the jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:55.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for me to fulfill such a demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:02.04,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, do you think we would believe the information you'd provide us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:04.04,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it would come to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:04.71,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:08.80,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll make you believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:20.35,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was alive, I was also good when it came to shoveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:21.73,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of man I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:27.82,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But what could Medusa be hiding in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:30.78,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:42.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:43.71,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:45.21,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,BREW!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:53.88,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:57.35,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The results of a thorough inspection tell us that this is the real BREW.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:01.85,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I will talk to her directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:05.56,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,According to her, it's about making a deal with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:07.94,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,A deal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:11.28,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, what could she have in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:14.28,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving up BREW so easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:19.78,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that Medusa possesses BREW also come at a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:21.37,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami-sama,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:24.79,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Undoubtedly she is planning to use Shibusen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:26.37,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It would appear so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:28.92,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:32.26,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I think there's the need for me to meet her in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.09,0:09:33.80,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:35.09,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:38.01,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to call her here immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:43.18,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:45.35,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:50.19,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see that you're in high spirits, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:53.61,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of what you did, the world is now in total disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:58.53,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I'd like to show you my gratitude for believing in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:01.12,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:04.91,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I'd like you to remove these restraints.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:10.25,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm standing in front of you, I don't think having it off will make any difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:16.01,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Those restraints, if you really wanted to remove them, you would have had them off long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:18.80,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be meaningless if I remove them myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:27.06,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do anything funny, I'll rip you to shreds without warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:34.19,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:37.90,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, Shinigami-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:42.37,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, one strike is the least she should have expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:47.29,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it! The attitude that I hate the most in Shibusen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:52.67,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Even during the time when I was still the nurse, I was trying desperately trying to adapt to this attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:57.47,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's this deal you are speaking of?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:10:58.80,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My panties...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:01.89,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, he's doing whatever he pleases.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:03.22,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I miscalculated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:06.31,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, can you please put me down?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:12.73,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Pumpkin panties?! Maka also wore that when she was still little.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:15.19,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:17.40,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting too weird,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:20.11,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I must somehow bring them to my pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:24.70,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's get back to the topi-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:27.70,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what it would look like if a woman wore bloomers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.08,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'd look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:32.21,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, in the past, they always wore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:35.63,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you think about it now, it kinda feels perverted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:38.59,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,They've started their own discussion on panties.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:41.34,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this nonsense right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:44.51,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it was rude of us to be talking about this in the presence of a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:46.85,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.27,0:11:49.68,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what is this deal you're speaking of?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:51.31,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Put me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:53.10,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Pumpkin panties!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:57.07,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If you continue doing that, I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:59.90,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What, can't even take some jokes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:04.62,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when "Repetition after repetition" is the fundamental of jokes, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:05.83,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You're talking about Tendon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:07.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. Tendon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:11.08,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case then let's do it three more times!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:13.04,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why is she backing up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:17.50,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm not going to pick you up by the hood anymore. Please come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:19.92,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:22.22,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:24.55,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,About the conditions of the deal,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:27.31,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,they aren't bad even from your stand point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:32.02,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,With that, you'll be able to find the answer to your biggest question right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:34.90,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What about if you stop making it sound so important and just tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:42.20,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't tell us right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:43.70,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pick you up by the hood again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:45.78,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already holding me by the hood!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:47.53,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Pumpkin panties!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:49.54,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Just stop this already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:53.16,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay! I'll tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:55.79,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:00.76,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,My card is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:04.47,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The location of the Kishin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:06.68,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:10.89,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Shibusen is putting all its effort in locating him and yet not a trace of him could be found anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:12.73,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That piece of information,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:16.48,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,can you prove to us that it isn't some kind of lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:17.86,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:21.15,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as I don't have your trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:22.65,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:25.40,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Then tell us the location!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.03,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:29.91,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not that stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:30.70,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:34.75,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Because if I tell you, then it wouldn't be a deal anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:37.21,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's the condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.63,0:13:39.09,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:45.38,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to guarantee me and my comrade's safety, as well as to release me from custody immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:47.97,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Just that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:49.85,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:55.60,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm... But I suppose that is a condition that I cannot accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:57.15,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:14:02.02,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,then I guess you'd rather choose to live your life in fear of Arachnophobia?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:03.65,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Arachne?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:04.65,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:08.36,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that Arachnophobia and the Kishin have some kind of relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:10.83,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll know soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:29.05,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:31.80,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:36.81,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:44.53,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll erase everything that makes you feel uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.28,0:14:46.99,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:52.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Mosquito.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:54.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:59.08,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,activating the madness amplifier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:51.13,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:53.93,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:56.31,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Please explain,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:58.31,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:02.77,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Arachne has taken in the Kishin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:04.86,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,And by using his power,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:08.07,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,she's trying to spread his insanity throughout the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:10.49,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pity, Medusa,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:12.99,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,with this, the deals off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:14.24,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:17.12,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a tremendous insanity wavelength,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:19.83,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,locating the source of the wavelength would be a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:23.17,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:24.00,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:27.63,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Arachne has set up relay stations all around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:31.42,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,The insanity wavelength's source has thus been cleverly hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:36.01,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If you look one-by-one, the world's going to be consumed by madness before you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:40.18,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Shinigami-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.60,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it? Or leave it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:49.94,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for a short while, would you give me some time to think about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:57.83,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Medusa's intentions are clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:02.21,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,She's trying incite a conflict between Shibusen and Arachnophobia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:09.00,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, she can just sit and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:11.67,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,If you already realize that, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:17.55,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I can't leave the situation the way as it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.10,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:21.52,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:23.60,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking about the same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:29.52,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Using the information she'd give us and wipe out the Kishin and Arachne both at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:34.57,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Or get rid of Medusa while it is still a simple task?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:37.87,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:41.37,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way they can turn down that offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:47.25,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:49.92,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I've won.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:56.68,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that's not how it turns out, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:04.98,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Which will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:20.53,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Medusa,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:28.37,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,you're free to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:36.55,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:37.88,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:39.22,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Maka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:43.39,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You should take a good look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:44.22,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:46.23,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll understand once you see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:47.48,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:49.56,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:55.57,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Medusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:58.86,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:00.95,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the details,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:04.79,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,but Shibusen has made a deal with Medusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.04,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:10.04,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:13.50,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Maka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:16.38,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:18.17,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,There will still be plenty of chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:25.10,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely beat the crap out of her, and when the time comes, I'll let you land a hit on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:05.22,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this how honorable father's going to do things?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:12.69,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:15.44,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do they let her go just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:17.07,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:21.53,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami, and Shibusen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:26.53,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,you shall become my pawns from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:44.14,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Stein?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:47.64,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Geeze, you didn't even turn on the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:54.02,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Stein?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:06.87,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Stein?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:13.58,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,Stein!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:23.63,SE,,0000,0000,0000,,And on that night.. Professor Stein disappeared.
